LINE.Text: Transition begins at noon on 23rd January. On the 24th easyJet's operation will be consolidated
into the North Terminal. The following day, British Airways begins operating entirely from the
South Terminal, having already moved two flights across early [BA2273 to New York from
11th January and BA2612 to Naples from 19th January). Also on the 25th, Virgin Atlantic will
relocate to the North Terminal. Here's what's happening over the critical 72-hour window.
